Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}だ…旦那様
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}老…老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}お…おかえりなさいませ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}您…您回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.61,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}私、出迎えもせず
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.61,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}未能出門迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}申し訳あり…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}實在抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}旦那様?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.82,0:20:21.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}老爺?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.62,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}美世、なぜだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.62,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}美世，為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}はい?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.62,0:20:24.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.25,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}なぜこんなにも痩せる?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.25,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}妳怎麼瘦成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.16,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}どうして倒れたことを隠す?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}為什麼不告訴我妳昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}それは…その…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.79,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}お前が夜な夜なうなされているのを
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}妳每天夜裡都在夢中呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.71,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}私が知らないと思うか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}以為我不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}私は言ったはずだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}我應該告訴過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}何でも言えと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}有話就說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.72,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}甘えろと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.72,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}別藏在心裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.93,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}だがいつまで経っても、お前は、何も…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.93,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}可無論過多久，妳都一言不發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}そんなに私が信用ならないか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&352A22\4c&352A22}我就這麼不值得信賴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}違います
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}旦那様の手を煩わせたくなかったのです
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}我不想為這種事勞煩您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}ただでさえお忙しくて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}您已經很忙碌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}疲れている旦那様を
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}每天都精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.94,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}私のことなんかで困らせたくなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an3\3c&664936\4c&664936}我不想再為您平添困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0}疲れているなどと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0}精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.95,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0}それはお前のほうだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.95,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0}那是妳才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}こんなことになるなら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}早知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}お前に勉強の機会など与えるのではなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我就不該讓妳去學習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.34,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}旦那様、ひどいです
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}老爺，妳好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}違う
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.38,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}こんなふうに…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&664936\4c&664936}我不是…
